frames.caption: A whimsical scene features miniature workers in yellow uniforms and hard hats, busily working on a giant lemon tart. The workers are using ladders and tools to sprinkle sugar and arrange lemon slices on the tart. Surrounding the scene are large, vibrant lemons hanging from branches.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature workers assembling a giant lemon tart. The workers, dressed in yellow uniforms, are using ladders to reach the top of the tart, which is adorned with a large lemon slice. The background features lush greenery and a bright, sunny sky.
frames.description: The scene is set in a fantastical kitchen-like environment where tiny figures are engaged in constructing a dessert.
